{"tid":215063,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"Paradox theory（奶油貓paradox+predestination paradox）","createTime":"2017-04-24T07:14:29.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-25T08:01:16.000Z","uid":73804,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"293dde0bd3e84cdd7f08740282665b48763cf214","tid":215063,"uid":73804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T07:14:29.000Z","msg":"今日睇到個幾得意既理論<br />\n首先奶油貓paradox包含左兩個既定既法則<br />\n<br />\n第一： 貓喺半空中跳下，永遠用腳著陸。<br />\n第二 ：將舊奶油西多拋到半空中，舊西多永遠喺搽左油嗰邊落地。<br />\n<br />\n而呢個paradox得意既地方係如果你將舊無搽油嗰邊黐住隻貓既背部，依照以上兩條定律，隻貓係唔可以用腳著陸，因為舊西多永遠喺搽左油嗰邊落地；但同樣地，搽左牛油嗰邊都落唔到地，因為隻貓永遠用腳著陸。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.kminer.net/2011/07/perpetual-motion/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.kminer.net%2F2011%2F07%2Fperpetual-motion%2F&d=ukYMMJnQLP7OtwhP8v88lBOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=067105e7\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.kminer.net/2011/07/perpetual-motion/</a><br />\n<br />\n呢個理論其實係apply左落磁浮列車度~<br />\n咁當然啦呢個理論係現實世界係隻貓會用腳landing而唔會一直飄浮，而呢樣野叫cat righting reflex，歡迎大家用自己隻貓試下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n下面繼續講第二個paradox<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/12.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52a4044524f1e69abf05d5cdafde10d7b7fabdbb","tid":215063,"uid":7275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"293dde0bd3e84cdd7f08740282665b48763cf214","tid":215063,"uid":73804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T07:14:29.000Z","msg":"今日睇到個幾得意既理論<br />\n首先奶油貓paradox包含左兩個既定既法則<br />\n<br />\n第一： 貓喺半空中跳下，永遠用腳著陸。<br />\n第二 ：將舊奶油西多拋到半空中，舊西多永遠喺搽左油嗰邊落地。<br />\n<br />\n而呢個paradox得意既地方係如果你將舊無搽油嗰邊黐住隻貓既背部，依照以上兩條定律，隻貓係唔可以用腳著陸，因為舊西多永遠喺搽左油嗰邊落地；但同樣地，搽左牛油嗰邊都落唔到地，因為隻貓永遠用腳著陸。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.kminer.net/2011/07/perpetual-motion/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.kminer.net%2F2011%2F07%2Fperpetual-motion%2F&d=ukYMMJnQLP7OtwhP8v88lBOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=067105e7\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.kminer.net/2011/07/perpetual-motion/</a><br />\n<br />\n呢個理論其實係apply左落磁浮列車度~<br />\n咁當然啦呢個理論係現實世界係隻貓會用腳landing而唔會一直飄浮，而呢樣野叫cat righting reflex，歡迎大家用自己隻貓試下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n下面繼續講第二個paradox<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/12.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T08:01:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}